Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.59,0:01:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.73,0:01:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些血 是你的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.32,0:02:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时真同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.12,0:02:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你身上都是血
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为你受了重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.33,0:02:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走? 要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第八话 人生在世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 你为什么会带刀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听了以后也会被卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望时真同学你遇到危险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也就说你现在身处险境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就更得知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁敲侧击 你呀是不会懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是 特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对我而言是特别的 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许也有我能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能答应我 不告诉任何人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜好好吃完了早饭就去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 她似乎很难过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又给唯芳先生添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:05:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜最喜欢爸爸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血 果然很重要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝咖啡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那喝别的 行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「古物」…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说 那东西会吃人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺和宁宁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有镇上的其他人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你的错 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我被选中要和「古物」战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打倒「古物」保护大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.53,0:06:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是没事的样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时真同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始 你为什么就抱我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是认真地在问我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有什么奇怪的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不就是这样的吗 现在的你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟也看到那些怪物了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是怪物 是「古物」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是执着于一些奇怪的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么叫都没差吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许…是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是简单擦擦 果然擦不干净呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧 我送你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想送你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来拿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你受伤了不是吗 刀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我自己拿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…时真同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好温柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想让大家都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时真同学是很温柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你知道就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼 今天的事就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可要是再有什么事 要告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉时真同学…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想知道 关于小夜的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 您怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不舒服吗 都是我没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我只是有点晕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是您的脸色…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 血…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.72,0:09:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身上的血沾到您身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 真的没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 千真万确
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲要是发生什么事的话 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道该做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该如何做才好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么看上去那么难过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲若难过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没精神 即使天气好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没精神 没精神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是身体不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是碍于在我面前 所以强撑着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不会「呀」「讨厌」这样尖叫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多已经好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己那伤口能迅速愈合的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.44,0:12:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 问了也白问
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么是和谁的约定 想起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你认为如果打破约定会怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「打倒古物 保护大家」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果打破了这个约定 会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 难得的实验
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦开始 就不得不决出胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且赏胜者 罚败者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你取胜 希望得到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.86,0:13:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果败了 被夺去什么能比死还痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不能倒下 我这个样子搬不动你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 不是这么简单就能想起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是应该用不了多久 恐怕马上…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.93,0:14:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我这就洗完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惩罚与奖赏…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后三天 「古物」也没有动静
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.75,0:15:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校通知 今天要复课
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.57,0:16:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不辛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只身一人和「古物」战斗 伤痕累累
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得辛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤很快就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 小夜很结实的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 还是要注意身体的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八卦中出现什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算接下来要出现的「古物」是强敌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也请不要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜一定打倒它回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像母亲那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「古物」出现的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把它消灭 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 你脸色不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.61,0:18:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎...像这个情况 也打不起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是诺诺还是宁宁都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像前几天 巡警先生也失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个镇没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更衣同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.03,0:18:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直停课 感觉好久没见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次见面虽然很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却感觉根本没办法静下心来上课
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前你也带这个来了 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:18:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面有个奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.43,0:19:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.06,0:19:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 好像动起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是个动作迟缓的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.56,0:19:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死…死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不打算让一个人逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更衣同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.09,0:21:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.47,0:21:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再让谁死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.37,0:23:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.44,0:23:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是浮岛神社的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.63,0:23:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个意思 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.61,0:23:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更衣小夜同学 这些全都是你杀的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.07,0:23:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话 Blood-C
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.13,0:23:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在心中


